subtitle: 2 Bedroom, 2 Bathroom, 1 kitchen
description: Welcome to the Yates on Yates by Chard development - this home offers wide plank, oak-inspired laminate flooring throughout with contemporary cabinetry, solid quartz counters and a spacious pantry. Within the home you'll find an integrated appliance package: counter-depth Liebherr fridge, Fisher/Paykel induction cooktop, built-in oven and panel front dishwasher drawer. With heated porcelain tile floors in the main bathroom, you'll feel cozy while maintaining a modern aesthetic by means of oversized windows and open floor plan. This home comes with an air cooling & heating system. You will enjoy the city landscape off your balcony in addition to the views out to the inner harbour from the rooftop patio. This area features BBQ's, kids play area & fenced dog run. Additionally there is parking, external storage, dog wash and a dedicated secure bike rack. The big bonus with this condo is the allocated green space off the balcony between the two building.
